## Licensing

The Adaptive Formula SDK uses a tiered licensing model.

* **Community (Free):** Ideal for small projects and testing.
    * Up to 1,000 evaluations per month.
    * Supports `dict` data format only.
    * Registration is required for production use.

* **Professional (Subscription):** For professional applications and small teams.
    * Unlimited evaluations.
    * Support for heterogeneous data (Pandas, NumPy).
    * ML-powered optimization capabilities.

* **Enterprise (Annual):** For mission-critical applications.
    * All features included.
    * Guaranteed support SLA and custom integrations.

To get a **Professional** or **Enterprise** license key, please contact `jaimeajl@hotmail.com` or visit `https://your-website.com/pricing`.

